                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "The second exam turned out to be significantly <w>easier</w> than the first."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Ему стало <w>легче</w> понимать иностранную речь после месяца практики.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "It became <w>easier</w> for him to understand foreign speech after a month of practice."
